{"tid":2000622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"嗰啲黃色經濟圈金剛棒bingo玩一次半次就好笑，個個post個個都貼洗版咁屌你老母 靜啦","createTime":"2020-05-04T03:54:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T05:53:47.000Z","uid":11598,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cda700f5d075a0804a3314965d584e9fcc1bd11a","tid":2000622,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T03:54:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚煩 拉落少少又有人貼<br />\n玩一次半次笑完咪算囉 越嚟越長 越貼越多<br />\n屌你老母"},{"pid":"8c149418b3d2de8a1df23f0edef6da511babfcaf","tid":2000622,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T03:55:55.000Z","msg":"貼撚夠未"},{"pid":"eb8e984c1954f7523b55ab3c720d67e6255f04b2","tid":2000622,"uid":6556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T04:00:56.000Z","msg":"條撚準備 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7af309cee3e439e784a93ad074320f218924e3d9","tid":2000622,"uid":11598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T04:05:07.000Z","msg":"成班傻閪淨係識得負評 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d3af89464984c2e4fa1de7f34dbfa7b62958db9","tid":2000622,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T05:53:47.000Z","msg":"關於黃色經濟圈，我有d野想講：<br />\n<br />\n我想講翻其實黃色經濟圈最核心精神係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>紅死藍貧，紅死是為了打擊支共呢個恐怖份子籌集資金。藍唔洗死，但要慘比其他綠絲睇，就係為左&ldquo;統戰&rdquo;綠絲，壯大黃色經濟圈。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n所以大家幫襯黃店之外亦要記得先紅後藍：<br />\n<br />\n1.切斷中國國企在香港經營獲得外匯收入的機會，以加速支爆。<br />\n2.令藍絲企業經營困難，&ldquo;統戰&rdquo;綠絲企業<br />\n舉例，呢個原則點樣用：<br />\n基於先紅後藍原則，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">銀行方面一定係先中銀後匯豐</span></strong><br />\n根據先紅後藍原則，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">應該先Pacific(華潤)後Starbucks（美心）</span></strong><br />\n基於先紅後藍原則，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>&ldquo;幫襯&rdquo;紅店力度不應該比藍店細。尤其各種隱性紅店係支共既重要回血劍</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n必須先紅後藍，否則中共恐成最後贏家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}